Jenni Evans, News24(ER24) Multimedia &nbsp; &nbsp; User Galleries &nbsp; &nbsp; News in Pictures Send us your pictures &nbsp; &nbsp; Send us your stories Durban &ndash; Two men escaped serious injury when a tree fell on their car in Hillcrest on Friday night, ER24 said on Saturday.When paramedics arrived at 20:00, they found the car with a large tree across its bonnet, said ER24 spokesperson Russel Meiring.One of the two men who had been in the car sustained minor injuries.He was treated on the scene and taken to a nearby hospital for further treatment.24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.